title: Welcome to my website!
text:
Welcome to my website!
I am an American board-certified in oral maxillofacial radiologyest. I am working in oral maxillofacial radiology department at CWRU School of Dental Medicine. Currently, I am a first year PhD student in Clinical Translation Science program in School of Medicine at Case Western Reserve University. My research interests lie at the intersection of cardiovascular disease and incidental findings in Cone beam Tomography.
On this website, you will find educational background, teaching and clinical experience, and my CV. On my CV I presented some of my published works. You will also find news and updates on my current situation. I invite you to explore my website and learn more about my lifeâ€™s work. Please feel free to contact me if you have any questions or would like to discuss potential projects.
